.TH "lsm_connect_timeout_set" 3 "lsm_connect_timeout_set" "February 2019" "Libstoragemgmt C API Manual" 
.SH NAME
lsm_connect_timeout_set \- Sets the time-out for this connection.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" lsm_connect_timeout_set
.BI "(lsm_connect *" conn ","
.BI "uint32_t " timeout ","
.BI "lsm_flag " flags ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "conn" 12
Valid lsm_connect pointer.
.IP "timeout" 12
Time-out in ms.
.IP "flags" 12
Reserved for future use, must be LSM_CLIENT_FLAG_RSVD.
.SH "VERSION"
1.0
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Sets the time-out for this connection.
.SH "RETURN"
Error code as enumerated by 'lsm_error_number'.
    * LSM_ERR_OK
        On success.
    * LSM_ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT
        When any argument is NULL or invalid lsm_connect or invalid
        flags.
